<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungngaih leh gitlohna ten ei um ui,
 Thihna a puih dingin;
 Ginnaa nunglam ka et kit leh,
 Ka Hukdampan ei hawl hi.

[V2]
 Nunnuom in ka kipak hi tu hin,
 Hukdampa nunnem leh Hehpihna chun;
 Ka lautha mang A hukdam tai.

[V3]
 2. Kipahna tak lunggila ka neih hi,
 Isu ei piek ahi;
 Leia sanga kipahna lienzaw'n,
 Van kipah nan ka dim hi.

[V4]
 3. Belam No lal lenna tang ka thillin,
 Kipah nan ei na muok;
 Thihna Jordan gal ka kaih tieng leh,
 Van guolvak lopi um ka.</lyrics>
<title>Isu Eipiek Ahi</title>
<hymn_number>97</hymn_number>
</song>